# Repository-specific DOC_SYNC rule extensions preserved across upgrade.
# Base file: .orch/rules/app/docsync.rules
app/internal/config,deploy/.env.runtime.example,deploy/.env.dev.example|docs/app/config.md,deploy/.env.runtime.example,deploy/.env.dev.example|config changes must update config docs and env examples
app/internal/transport/httpapi/v1,app/openapi|docs/app/api.md,app/openapi/openapi.yaml|api routes and contract changes must update docs and contract
app/internal/transport/httpapi/httpx/envelope.go,app/internal/transport/httpapi/httpx/request_context.go,app/internal/transport/httpapi/middleware|docs/app/api.md|http envelope and middleware behavior changes must update docs/app/api.md
app/internal/service/example,app/internal/infra/store/postgres,app/db/migrations,app/internal/runtime,app/internal/worker,app/internal/transport/httpapi/router.go|docs/app/architecture.md|domain, storage, runtime, worker, and router wiring changes must update architecture docs
app/internal/service/shared,app/internal/transport/httpapi/httpx/errors.go,app/internal/transport/httpapi/middleware/drain.go,app/internal/transport/httpapi/middleware/request_timeout.go,app/internal/transport/httpapi/middleware/recover.go|docs/app/errors.md|error baseline changes must update docs/app/errors.md
